data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. CONGRATULATIONS!! This Beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom luxury series townhome is located in the beautiful gated Copper Chase community in Oviedo. This community is zoned for some of the best rated public elementary, middle, and high schools in Central Florida. This community is in walking distance of Publix, LA Fitness, Starbucks, Chic Fil A, Oviedo in the Park and a brand new Sprouts and Marshalls. This is a beautiful unit. It has a beautiful covered front patio along with rear patio, perfect for outdoor grilling. This unit sits a few homes away from the playground which has a beautiful view of the water. As you walk into this townhome you’ll love the beautiful tile floors. To the right you’ll walk into the kitchen, great room, and dining area which are extremely comforting and inviting and has the most amazing lighting. To the left is your first floor 1/2 bath. When you walk upstairs you’ll enter a large foyer hallway area. To the left you’ll walk into a large Owner’s suite with a beautiful sitting area, large walk-in closet, and large master bath. This home is a must see.
